messages.speech: Information on BC Ferries can be found here: BC Ferries are operating at reduced capacty and non-essential travel is not advised.  More information can be found here: https://www.bcferries.com/current_conditions/travel-advisory.html?bcgovtm=20200319_GCPE_AM_COVID_4_NOTIFICATION_BCGOV_BCGOV_EN_BC__NOTIFICATION
